# Redirects configuration for Cloudflare Pages
# Place this file in your public/ directory
# Max 2000 static + 100 dynamic redirects

# Force HTTPS (if using custom domain)
# http://tim.current.space/* https://tim.current.space/:splat 301

# Remove www (if applicable)
# https://www.tim.current.space/* https://tim.current.space/:splat 301

# Old URL redirects (examples)
# /old-page /new-page 301
# /blog/* /news/:splat 301

# Note: Cloudflare Pages automatically handles SPA routing
# The fallback to index.html happens by default for non-existent paths
# No need for /* /index.html 200 rule